  <description><![CDATA[<p>Montecatini Terme is surrounded by glorious Tuscan countryside. Elegant hotels line the avenues, interspersed with restaurants, shops and pavement cafés. Visit the spectacular Tettuccio spa, enjoy a free evening classical music concert, hop on a train to Pescia and stroll in the Tuscan countryside, Montecatini is a mature, established <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/italy" title="Italian">Italian</a> resort town with plenty going on. A funicular railway links the centre to the hilltop village of Montecatini Alto where you can enjoy stunning views over the town and the plains beyond. Your holiday in Montecatini means you are ideally placed for sightseeing with frequent bus and train services, so towns such as <a data-udi="umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b}" title="Florence">Florence</a>, Pisa and Lucca are all within easy reach.</p>
<p>Inghams operate a telephone Rep service in Montecatini.</p>]]></description>
