  <resortCombinations><![CDATA[<p>TUSCAN &amp; UMBRIAN EXPERIENCE</p>
<p><br />Combine your holiday in Montecatini with a stay on Lake Trasimeno so you can experience the beauty and diversity of both areas.</p>
<p><strong>Montecatini</strong> Explore the Tuscan countryside and the famous cities of Florence and Pisa, wander through the side streets of San Gimignano and Siena as well as sample the local Chianti wines.</p>
<p><strong>Lake Trasimeno</strong> is set in the heart of Umbria. The resort of Passignano gives you a tranquil location with lake side promenades and stunning sunsets over the lake. The town is relaxed and traditionally Italian and has great access to visit local villages like Cortona and Assisi steeped in fascinating history.</p>
<p>YOUR HOTELS<br />Montecatini (7 nights ) Grand Hotel Plaza <br />Lake Trasimeno (7 nights) Hotel Lido <br />from £1,199 per person</p>
<p>WHAT’S INCLUDED</p>
<ul>
<li>Return flights to Pisa from the UK on Wednesdays &amp; Saturdays</li>
<li>Transfers by coach between resorts and the airport</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></resortCombinations>
